        "Keep onBindViewHolder lightweight",
        "Use View Binding in ViewHolder"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "heading": "Summary",
      "content": "RecyclerView efficiently displays large datasets using view recycling and flexible layouts. Combined with ListAdapter and DiffUtil, it provides smooth scrolling and efficient UI updates."
